information: Marsol Fruits Spain S.L. is a company specialising in the fruit and vegetable trade from the countryside in Murcia and Almeria. We guarantee a professional service and efficient management of products from purchase, and ensure that the quality, price and packing satisfy your expectations. We also provide logistics if you wish. We provide the best quality at the best price. We specialise in different varieties of lettuce (Iceberg, Cos, Little Gem), broccoli, artichokes, cauliflowers, cucumbers, Dutch cucumbers, different varieties of tomato (long shelf life, Rebellion, on-the-vine, olivettes), lemons, oranges, mandarins, different varieties of sweet peppers (California, Lamuyo), etc. We obtain our supplies from the main selling areas and market high quality produce in the national and European market.
